title: Out of 25pcs 2 no's damage material sent
body: I expected good and professional services but out of 25pcs 2pcs damage products were sent but I didn't return as it was for my personal use. I adjusted.. I hope the seller will personally look into the matter and no further damages will be sent for other buyers.

title: 'Not the quality you expect.'
body: For starters, the product was delivered 2 days late and through DTDC. Second, the packaging was extremely poor. It was torn from one end. The files are of decent quality. It's very thin as compared to what you might expect it to be.
